foreign.xhtml:div:
2.In this Act -
"arms" means any coat of arms, crest, seal or other armorial bearing, other than a specified emblem;
"the College of Arms" means the College of Arms established by section 3 of this Act;
"design", in relation to arms, means the design of the arms and the nature of any device thereon and any words or signs written thereon;
"specified emblem" has the meaning assigned to it in the National Flag. Emblems and Names Act.
